Liliwen is an Elven farmer living in the Elven village of Lletya. She watches over the Lletya fruit tree patch. In exchange for a range of possible payments, she will watch over players' crops and prevent them from dying, eliminating the need for regular monitoring of the patch.

Shop[edit | edit source]

Liliwen also sells basic farming tools, which can be accessed by talking to her and asking Can you sell me something? It is not an actual shop and it has no set stock; each item must be bought individually through the dialogue.
